### Marketvesitario - API Tests
### Extensión requerida: REST Client (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

# ================================================================
# AUTH - REGISTRO
# ================================================================

### Registrar nuevo estudiante
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "estudiante@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234!",
  "nombres": "Maria",
  "apellidos": "Lopez",
  "tipo_documento": "CC",
  "documento_identidad": "1234567890",
  "programa_academico": "Ingenieria de Sistemas"
}

###

### Registrar sin campo obligatorio (debe retornar error 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "incompleto@test.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

###

### Registrar con contraseña corta (debe retornar error 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "otro@test.com",
  "password": "123",
  "nombres": "Juan",
  "apellidos": "Perez",
  "tipo_documento": "CC",
  "documento_identidad": "9876543210"
}

###

# ================================================================
# AUTH - LOGIN
# ================================================================

### Login exitoso (usando estudiante de la bd local)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "estudiante@marketvesitario.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

###

### Login fallido (contraseña incorrecta)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "estudiante@marketvesitario.com",
  "password": "mal"
}

###
